🏠 Tenant Functionalities (PAMS System)
🔐 1. Login & Dashboard Access
Tenants should be able to:
* Log in securely to their personal account
* Access a personal dashboard
* Only see their own data (not other tenants)



👤 2. View Personal Tenant Profile
Tenants can:
* View their personal details (name, email, phone, occupation, NI number)
* View assigned apartment details:
    * Location
    * Type (1-bed, 2-bed, etc.)
    * Monthly rent
    * Lease start & end date

💷 3. Payments & Billing
Tenants can:
✔ View payment history
* All past payments
* Due payments
* Late payments status
✔ Make payments (simulated)
* Enter card details (validation only — no real processing)
* System creates a payment record:
    * Date
    * Amount
    * Status (Paid / Failed / Late)
✔ View invoices / dues
* Monthly rent due
* Outstanding balances

⏰ 4. Late Payment Alerts
System should:
* Automatically flag late payments
* Show alerts on dashboard:
    * “Payment overdue”
    * “Late fee applied (if applicable)”

🛠️ 5. Maintenance Requests
Tenants can:
✔ Submit repair request
* Describe issue
* Select category (plumbing, electricity, etc.)
* Submit request
✔ Track request progress
* Status updates:
    * Pending
    * In progress
    * Assigned worker
    * Completed

⚠️ 6. Complaints System
Tenants can:
* Submit complaints (noise, staff, building issues, etc.)
* View complaint status
* See resolution updates

📊 7. Graphical Dashboard Features (VERY IMPORTANT)
Tenants should see visual analytics:
📈 Payment history graph
* Shows payments over time
📉 Late payment chart
* Shows how many payments were late per property
🏘️ Comparison graph (advanced requirement)
* Tenant payments vs “close neighbours”
    * (e.g. same building or same apartment type average)

🏡 8. Lease & Apartment Info
Tenants can:
* View lease agreement details
* See lease end date
* Check rent amount
* View apartment assignment

🧾 9. Notifications System
Dashboard should notify tenants about:
* Upcoming rent due dates
* Late payments
* Maintenance updates
* Complaint updates

🚪 10. Early Lease Termination Request
Tenants can:
* Request to leave before contract ends
* System rules:
    * Must give 1 month notice
    * Must pay 5% penalty of monthly rent
* System calculates penalty automatically
